{"tid":1150102,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[想笑下] 一人一個最高質的笑話。","createTime":"2019-05-11T15:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T02:02:14.000Z","uid":34773,"like":23,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"08ead6f867d803e66ec1c330fc6f65ebac2dc73d","tid":1150102,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:03:38.000Z","msg":"和尚叫雞<br />\n深圳臭雞：不好意思，我不想做和尚生意。<br />\n老納：我都無厭棄你係雞，你竟然厭棄我呢個純潔o既出家人？<br />\n深圳臭雞：你是真和尚？<br />\n老納：真和尚假和尚真係係咁重要咩? 你會唔會過問每一個割咗包皮o既客人，<br />\n怕佢係天主教徒? 怕佢係一個Father?<br />\n深圳臭雞：算啦算啦，不要那麼多廢話，把你的袈裟脫下。<br />\n老納：見我同施主有緣，等老納我就即刻扲條嘢出嚟啦！<br />\n深圳臭雞：不要呀，要先洗澡！<br />\n老納：你心境污穢， 佢先係一條撚， 如果你心境好，佢就係一條善根。你放埋落口，仲可以積口<br />\n德，放落陰道，就可以積陰德。"},{"pid":"8a7d50284695f6cfd3ec0bf85ec95672655f91bb","tid":1150102,"uid":50744,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:13:04.000Z","msg":"我認我笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6faabf0ae3011fdc07c1e906ba280048f083718a","tid":1150102,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:14:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真係頭條笑話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係幾有哲學性<br />\n觀點與角度</span>"},{"pid":"4131b32013f7268c722e2622ba0065a4313cc852","tid":1150102,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6faabf0ae3011fdc07c1e906ba280048f083718a","tid":1150102,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:14:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真係頭條笑話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係幾有哲學性<br />\n觀點與角度</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.... 認真少少ok?"},{"pid":"5d478a19dade50aba45e0220e1beb8e42d3a9be9","tid":1150102,"uid":218619,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:25:54.000Z","msg":"基圍蝦<br />\n<br />\n基基基基基<br />\n基基基基基<br />\n基基蝦基基<br />\n基基基基基<br />\n基基基基基<br />\n<br />\n利申: chin u 